This follows after Thu Nguyen, a nonbinary council member, decided to take at least 30 days to process the fact that she/he/they was misgendered.

Last night, Worcester, Massachusetts voted to become a “Sanctuary City for Transgender and Gender Diverse People”

description:
When you are a five-year-old and it's your birthday, you want toys. You want Spider-Man or one of the PAW Patrol pups to show up. You want a bounce house. You want to overdose on sugar. Poor Vivek Vance got stuck spending his birthday at a work event for his parents and was NOT happy about it. He doesn't care who knows it either, in a photo that makes the Vice President and the Second Lady THE most relatable couple in all of the United States of the Americas.

This also makes it only a matter of time before the journalisming industry use the Vance kids as part of their political attacks.

JD Vance made his first overseas trip as Vice President on Monday to an AI Summit in Paris. While Vivek didn't get a visit from Spider-Man, he did hang out with Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi.
title: JD Vance's son mean-mugging the camera while forced to spend his birthday with India's PM takes over the Internet
